r><![CDATA[John Appleseed]]></dc:creator><category><![CDATA[Drinks]]></category></item><item><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.zegelin.com/recipes/Recipes/Drinks/Margarita</guid><title>Margarita</title><link>https://www.zegelin.com/recipes/Recipes/Drinks/Margarita</link><description><![CDATA[notes:The Margarita has suffered terribly in modern times. In an effort to make it hip, quick, trendy and cheap it has been bastardized far worse then any cocktail before it. Whether it is the use of inferior (or just plain wrong) ingredients, or commercially made mixes, the common Margarita these days tastes more like a ‘Limeade’ with a splash of orange juice than it does the delectable cocktail that it once was.]]></description><pubDate>Sun, 15 Sep 2024 12:31:28 +1000</pubDate><dc:creator><![CDATA[John Appleseed]]></dc:creator><category><![CDATA[Drinks]]></category></item><item><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.zegelin.com/recipes/Recipes/Drinks/Mojito</guid><title>Mojito</title><link>https://www.zegelin.com/recipes/Recipes/Drinks/Mojito</link><description><![CDATA[notes:This traditional Cuban cocktail became popular in the United States during the late 1980’s and has recently seen a resurgence in popularity.]]></description><pubDate>Sun, 15 Sep 2024 12:31:28 +1000</pubDate><dc:creator><![CDATA[John Appleseed]]></dc:creator><category><![CDATA[Drinks]]></category></item><item><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.zegelin.com/recipes/Recipes/BBQ/BBQ_Chicken_With_Spicy_Honey_Bacon_Glaze</guid><title>BBQ Chicken With Spicy Honey Bacon Glaze</title><link>https://www.zegelin.com/recipes/Recipes/BBQ/BBQ_Chicken_With_Spicy_Honey_Bacon_Glaze</link><description><![CDATA[notes:Serves: 2]]></description><pubDate>Sun, 15 Sep 2024 12:31:28 +1000</pubDate><dc:creator><![CDATA[John Appleseed]]></dc:creator><category><![CDATA[BBQ]]></category></item><item><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.zegelin.com/recipes/Recipes/BBQ/Middle_Eastern_Chicken_Skewers</guid><title>Middle Eastern Chicken